        </ul>
      </nav>
      <button
        class="text-sm font-medium text-white border border-white px-3 py-2 rounded"
      >
        ENG ▼
      </button>
    </header>
    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20">
        <img
          src="\hola3.jpg"
          alt="Profile"
          width="200"
          height="200"
          class="rounded-full mx-auto mb-8"
        />
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-balance mb-4">
          Hey! I'm <span id="name-container"></span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6 serif">
          The <strong>Software</strong> Developer
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-gray-400">
          <strong>With 4+ years</strong> of programming study, I <strong
            >specialize</strong
          > in web development but have a <strong>passion</strong> for all aspects
          of coding. I'm currently <strong>exploring opportunities</strong> as a
          backend, frontend, or QA developer. With a <strong
            >solid foundation</strong
          > in coding and a broad skill set, I'm ready to bring <strong
            >value and happiness</strong
          > to your team.
        </p>
        <button
          class="bg-transparent hover:bg-white text-white font-semibold hover:text-black py-2 px-4 border border-white hover:border-transparent rounded mb-6"
        >
          Download CV
        </button>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
          <a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
            <i class="fab fa-github fa-lg"></i>
          </a>
