              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">More about me</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div
            class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 col-span-1 md:col-span-2"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center">
              <i class="fas fa-briefcase mr-2"></i>
              At Work
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Details about your work experience and professional
              achievements...
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 row-span-2"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center">
              <i class="fas fa-user mr-2"></i>
              My personal side
